{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Example: Banking systems, CRMs, ERP platforms.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Use NoSQL Databases When:\par}
