{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The data is unstructured or semi-structured.\line \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Example: Social networks, IoT platforms, content management, analytics.\sa180\par}
